nt to come too near in case we're sucked in and have to share it.\n\n- Elizabeth Goudge, The Scent of Water\n|\nColonel: Tell me what is the T.R.U.T.H, Doctor!Doctor: Total.Reveal.Using.Therapeutic.Hologram\n\n- Toba Beta, Betelgeuse Incident: Insiden Bait Al-Jauza\n|\nIt's just... You sound like lorde. But like, with maple syrup.\n\n- Moriah McStay, Everything That Makes You"